data.title: Orem Utah ZIP Codes - Map and Full List
data.meta_description: List and Interactive Map of All ZIP Codes in Orem Utah
data.text:
Orem Utah is covered by a total of 3 ZIP Codes. There are also 2 ZIP Codes that overlap Orem but have a different postal city name. The ZIP Codes in Orem range from 84057 to 84604. Of the ZIP codes within or partially within Orem there are 3 Standard ZIP Codes. The total population of ZIP Codes in Orem is 94247.

Click on the ZIP Codes in the interactive map to view more information. The map control in the upper right corner can be used to toggle map layers on and off. The red outline is the border of Orem and can be turned on and off. Each type of postal code can also be turned on and off.
